Tracks.csv

Data included

A list of the tracks, playlists and radio stations in your Google Play Music library, as well as your playback and search history.

More options to manage your privacy

Google Account

Manage your info, privacy and make Google work better for you
Below are all the possible formats that you could have received in your archive:
Playlist
All metadata and track metadata associated with a playlist.
CSV
The CSV contains the following columns: Title, Owner, Description, Shared, Deleted
Radio Station
All metadata associated with a radio station.
CSV
The CSV contains the following columns for a curated radio station: Title, Curator, Description, Artists on this station, Similar Stations. The .csv contains the following columns for an algorithmic radio station: Title, Artist, Description, Artists on this station, Similar Stations. The .csv contains the following columns for an algorithmic radio station from an unmatched track: Title, Artist, Description.
Track
All metadata associated with a track.
CSV
The CSV contains the following columns: Title, Album, Artist, Duration (ms), Rating, Play Count
